payload_description.name: bootType
payload_description.description:
Boot type system
0-Unknown
1-Cold Start
2-Watchdog
3-Hardware reset
4-Hardware backup
5-Software backup
6-Software reset
7-VIO fail
8-VDD_X fail
9-VDD_RF fail
10-V_CORE_HIGH fail
11-System reset
